# LoRA/QLoRA 训练产物：体积大（单文件常超 GitHub 100MB 限制），不进版本控制
customer-service-qlora/saves/**/*.safetensors
customer-service-qlora/saves/**/*.pt
customer-service-qlora/saves/**/*.pth
customer-service-qlora/saves/**/checkpoint-*/

# LLaMA-Factory 源码（从 GitHub clone 得到，不需要跟着项目一起提交）
customer-service-qlora/LLaMA-Factory/

# 本机推理验证用的临时环境：venv、下载的基座模型权重、日志
customer-service-qlora/_local_infer/venv/
customer-service-qlora/_local_infer/models/
customer-service-qlora/_local_infer/*.log
customer-service-qlora/_local_infer/__pycache__/

# customer-http-demo：venv 和运行日志不进版本控制
customer-http-demo/venv/
customer-http-demo/*.log
customer-http-demo/__pycache__/
